Subject: Midwest Mash: Whiskies of the Great Lakes
Description:
There are a significant number of craft distilleries in the Midwest region, come and hear what makes them unique from each other, how those whiskies are made. Then stay for a tasting! The presentation will be open, but the tasting will be limited attendance. 21+ and ID will be required. Please sign up in advance at Ops.
  Speakers include:Greg Williams - Track: Food  - Duration: 1 hour and 50 minutes
